{"name": "odoo14-addon-mass-mailing-subscription-email", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-mass-mailing-subscription-email", "version": "14.0.1.0.4", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/social", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo"], "summary": "Send notification emails when contacts subscription changes.", "upload_time": 1698476739}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fsocial-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/social\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/social/tree/14.0/mass_mailing_subscription_email\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/social-14-0/social-14-0-mass_mailing_subscription_email\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/social&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n  maintainer-ivantodorovich: |-\n    ```{image} https://github.com/ivantodorovich.png?size=40px\n    :alt: ivantodorovich\n    :target: https://github.com/ivantodorovich\n    ```\n---\n\n# Mass Mailing Subscription Email\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:64dbf4395fcd768aa0bf2dfba65977a775ae389e5e05520d491cedc4918b6782\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nSend notification emails when contacts are subscribed or unsubscribed to mailing lists.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Configuration\n\nOn the mailing list record, configure the subscribe and unsubscribe email templates.\nIf you leave them empty, the feature is disabled.\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/social/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/social/issues/new?body=module:%20mass_mailing_subscription_email%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Camptocamp\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Camptocamp](https://www.camptocamp.com)\n\n  > - Iv\u00e1n Todorovich \\<<mailto:ivan.todorovich@gmail.com>>\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nCurrent [maintainer](https://odoo-community.org/page/maintainer-role):\n\n{{ maintainer-ivantodorovich }}\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/social](https://github.com/OCA/social/tree/14.0/mass_mailing_subscription_email) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute.